  "detailed_description": "<h1>WISHLIST</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/f29a07b9c20caf66ed7a88e27bb93767.poster.avif?t=1748002763\" width=616 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/f29a07b9c20caf66ed7a88e27bb93767.webm?t=1748002763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/87c9e68f8886b4a89103903f839c99fa.poster.avif?t=1748002763\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/87c9e68f8886b4a89103903f839c99fa.webm?t=1748002763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/87c9e68f8886b4a89103903f839c99fa.mp4?t=1748002763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the old castle of the renowned inventor Heinrich Von Schinker, in northern England, Heinrich's spirit returns as a small ghost. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alongside a mysterious bubble that he can move with gentle blows, he must face his own out-of-control inventions and fierce wild animals. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guiding the bubble to freedom is his only goal. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/d4d0e957cbf08f46f9e880bc47222879.poster.avif?t=1748002763\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/d4d0e957cbf08f46f9e880bc47222879.webm?t=1748002763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/d4d0e957cbf08f46f9e880bc47222879.mp4?t=1748002763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/839c455f33a9b89b5d25565f5bc3254a.avif?t=1748002763\" width=600 height=94 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Challenge Your Skills</strong></h2>Overcome levels filled with dangers and puzzles that will test your abilities. With addictive gameplay and devilish difficulty, your only goal is to protect the bubble at all costs.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/99a0a886121b96c73a615c15603bd815.poster.avif?t=1748002763\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/99a0a886121b96c73a615c15603bd815.webm?t=1748002763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/99a0a886121b96c73a615c15603bd815.mp4?t=1748002763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Defeat Epic Bosses</strong></h2>Face fierce bosses that will make you sweat. Only the most skilled will emerge victorious.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/c221ce9d1ab8f4f6eff0a5955d9bbccd.poster.avif?t=1748002763\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/c221ce9d1ab8f4f6eff0a5955d9bbccd.webm?t=1748002763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/c221ce9d1ab8f4f6eff0a5955d9bbccd.mp4?t=1748002763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Relive the Original Classic</strong></h2>Enjoy the full remaster of the 90s game, with 36 original levels recreated with completely renewed art.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/52c5225f53cb6269688ab3e7d78ea2c3.poster.avif?t=1748002763\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/52c5225f53cb6269688ab3e7d78ea2c3.webm?t=1748002763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/52c5225f53cb6269688ab3e7d78ea2c3.mp4?t=1748002763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Compete for Glory</strong></h2>Perfect your times in speedrun mode and submit your results online to secure your place in the prestigious Hall of Fame.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/02b59b584f2bb3d6bd7f31664e756920.poster.avif?t=1748002763\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/02b59b584f2bb3d6bd7f31664e756920.webm?t=1748002763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/02b59b584f2bb3d6bd7f31664e756920.mp4?t=1748002763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/92710796a42cb33dcbc2cb58da029133.avif?t=1748002763\" width=600 height=94 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Enjoy an adventure with over 40 levels filled with skill and clever puzzles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Three difficulty levels tailored to your playstyle.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Completely revamped graphics and sound that bring the magical world of the castle to life.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Dive deep into Heinrich's story by finding hidden collectibles throughout the castle chambers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Upload your scores and compare them with the best players worldwide in the online ranking.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Discover secret rooms, alternative endings, and unlock challenging in-game achievements.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/b48c0de135cfbb51fb39414fa9d662ed.poster.avif?t=1748002763\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/b48c0de135cfbb51fb39414fa9d662ed.webm?t=1748002763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/b48c0de135cfbb51fb39414fa9d662ed.mp4?t=1748002763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/7f1e983f789d702d44283a05973b85c1.avif?t=1748002763\" width=600 height=110 /></span></p></li></ul>",
